author: Lauren Ingram For Daily Mail Australia
title: Woman who ate KFC almost EVERY DAY loses 45 kilograms | Daily Mail Online
text: Woman who ate KFC up to FIVE times a week ballooned to 145kg before losing 45kg in only six months - as she reveals how she did it Kirby McGregor used to eat KFC almost every day and gained a lot of weight The 28-year-old weighed 145 kilograms and had numerous health problems Doctors told her she needed to lose weight to reduce swelling on her brain Ms McGregor has now lost a huge 45 kilograms in only six months She says she wants to lose another 20 kilograms to 'feel like the old me'
